"""Test modify_resource."""
message = self.common.modify_resource(self.data.array, 'sloprovisioning',
    'storagegroup', {})
self.assertEqual(self.data.job_list[0], message)
message_1 = self.common.modify_resource(category='sloprovisioning',
    resource_level='storagegroup', resource_level_id=self.data.array)
self.assertEqual(self.data.job_list[0], message_1)
